                <div id="contentBox" style="font: 400 14px Open Sans, Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; color: #3e3e3e; width: 96%; padding: 10px 2%; background: #FFF; text-align: justify; border-top: 1px dashed #ff530d; margin-bottom: 0px; float: left; overflow: hidden;">
                    <h2>
                        <p style="color: red;">Solo-fessional: Solo Katsu Danshi to Bocchi Joshi no Koubou-sen summary: </p>
                    </h2>
                    Hasama Shin is a solo guy who loves being alone. He even changed jobs to enjoy his time alone after coming home, and one day, a girl living in the apartment next door asks him if he wants to hang out with her. &quot;It&#039;s creepy that she asked me out on our first meeting, and more than anything, I don&#039;t have time for other people! ...Or so I thought, but I was tempted and ended up hanging out with her, and she started following me around every day...?!&quot; A comedy about the struggle between a solo guy and a lonely girl!! (Source: YanMaga Web, translated)
                </div>

